# Encounter Henley Prayer Room Insights

This repository contains the codebase for the Prayer Room Insights dashboard. It provides analytics on prayer sessions, user participation, and specific "Pray Day" events.

## Accessing the Dashboard

The dashboard is accessible online at: [https://prayerstats.encounteradelaide.com.au](https://prayerstats.encounteradelaide.com.au)

## Documentation

-   **Deployment & Usage:** See [DEPLOYMENT.md](DEPLOYMENT.md) for instructions on how to access the live site, upload data, and deploy updates.
-   **Flask Application:** An alternative Flask implementation is located in the `flask_project/` directory. See `flask_project/README.md` for details.

## Quick Start (Local Development)

To run the Streamlit application locally:

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
python -m streamlit run dashboard_app.py
```

## Project Structure

-   `dashboard_app.py`: The main Streamlit application source code.
-   `prayer_analytics_lib.py`: Core library containing data processing and analysis logic.
-   `flask_project/`: Directory containing the Flask implementation.
-   `gwop.csv`, `current.csv`: Data files used for analysis.
-   `passenger_wsgi.py`: Entry point for cPanel/Passenger deployment.
